                                        <head>
                                            <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                                        </head>
                                        <p>The information set forth above is derived from the
                                            American minutes of the meeting prepared by <persName corresp="#p_BATTLELC1">Lucius D. Battle</persName>.
                                            The <persName corresp="#p_BATTLELC1">Battle</persName>
                                            minutes, comprising some nine wide-margined pages of
                                            manuscript, contain no reference to any subject not
                                            covered in the telegraphic report printed <hi rend="italic">infra</hi>. The original copy of the
                                                <persName corresp="#p_BATTLELC1">Battle</persName>
                                            minutes is included in Conference files, lot 59 D 95, CF
                                            103. Another copy of the <persName corresp="#p_BATTLELC1">Battle</persName> minutes is
                                            included in <gloss target="#t_CFM1">CFM</gloss> files,
                                            lot M 88, box 161, “London–Lisbon, Misc.”</p>
